[src:visual-basic-net/visual-basic-net] They assume that the developer has created a form, placed a button on it and has associated the subroutines demonstrated in each example with the click event handler of the mentioned button.
[src:visual-basic-net/visual-basic-net] Each example creates a "Hello, World" message box after the button on the form is clicked.
